== Bio 

Previously I was a research assistant at [https://www.math.ust.hk Department of Mathematics] of [https://www.ust.hk The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology (HKUST)], under the supervision of Prof. [https://www.math.ust.hk/~yuany/ Yuan Yao] and Prof. [http://www.math.ust.hk/~jfcai/ Jian-Feng Cai]. I worked towards my master research under the supervision of [http://www-syscom.univ-mlv.fr/~chouzeno/ Emilie Chouzenoux] and [https://pesquet.info/ Jean-Christophe Pesquet] at [https://www.centralesupelec.fr/ CentraleSupélec], Université Paris-Saclay, France. I completed my previous degrees at HKUST and [https://hku.hk The University of Hong Kong (HKU)] respectively. 
Please refer to my [pdf/cv/cv_lau_tsz_kit_simple.pdf résumé] for further details. 

